subtitle: a centenary memorial
title: Charlotte Brontë; 1816-1916
by_statement: prepared by the Brontë society, ed. by Butler Wood, F. R. S. L., with a foreword by Mrs. Humphry Ward and 3 maps and 28 illustrations.

notes.value:
"First published in 1917; second impression, 1918."
